New Website, Who Dis?

February 13, 2023 · One min read

[Felix Boehm]

Felix Boehm

Maintainer of Cheerio

[]

Cheerio has a new website, and it's looking pretty good! This has been in the works for a while, and
we're excited to finally share it with you. Let's walk through all that's new.

[]note

Cheerio's website is still a work-in-progress, and covers Cheerio's next release that isn't available
yet. We would love your help in making this website better!

