each() <L=e#8c></L><I=8c>
  each <  T  >(  this  ,  fn  ):  Cheerio  <  T  >

Defined in: src/api/traversing.ts:640

Iterates over a cheerio object, executing a function for each matched element. When the callback is
fired, the function is fired in the context of the DOM element, so  this  refers to the current element,
which is equivalent to the function parameter  element  . To break out of the  each  loop early, return
with  false  .

